member.example:
 An application can use this method in a button press for an image capture.

private void button1_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)
{
    ImageData image = MyImager.CaptureImageNow();
}

 An application can use this method in a button press for an image capture.

private void button1_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)
{
     //open imager using the first available device
     MyImager = new Imaging2(); 
     //Save image to a file.
     ImageData image = MyImager.CaptureImageNow("MyImage_2.jpg", true);


}

An application can use this method after attaching an event handler to execute after a
trigger is pulled for an image capture.

MyImager.OnCapture += new Imaging2.OnCaptureHandler(MyImager_OnCapture);
MyImager.CaptureImage();

An application can use this method after attaching an event handler to execute after a
